{
  "stem": "25348.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on holidays-- during holidays or approaching holidays, such as Christmas and Easter, you would have academics and students, Poles, called Endecks, from the nearby higher institutions.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was customary to gang up before the shop and stop the customers from going into the kosher butcher.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because it wasn't frequented only by Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm not sure whether-- how kosher this butcher was, but I had no perception, you know, of, of being more kosher than-- or less kosher.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I knew we were Jewish, and we're using that meat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And this store was frequented by non-Jews also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family was more traditional, though I-- and this came-- perhaps my father was religious, but this came because the family split up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had hired help to run the household.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I would say that it wasn't a kosher household, but, but yes, we were observant in the sense that there was a lot of commotion back home, for example, at Pesach.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they used to get the dishes and-- for Pesach, they were specially packed in special boxes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to get them down from the attics, kind of, to use them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, and back they went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was quite a big thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and you say whether I ever experienced anti-Semitism-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not in a way, you know, where you were engaged in discussions as a little girl with, with people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my grandparents lived [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] about an hour and a quarter-- about, yes-- from Lwow in a small shtetl.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it was quite picturesque.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The, the station was quite picturesque.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it had flowers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, and I got off the station, off the train, to go to my grandparents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And there were some Polish ladies there.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
